Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:28.27,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kimi to ima hitotsu ni nareru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:31.22,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}oitsukenai hodo no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.13,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}chikara te ni irete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:38.62,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kaze wo kitte tsuranuite yuke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.11,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}dare wo shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.77,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}tsuujiaeta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:48.67,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kiseki okoseru nando demo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:53.66,Roman,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}shinjitsu itsuka mieru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:49.41,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}When I'm overcome by thoughts of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.86,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Clearly reflecting your motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:56.08,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}My eyes are filled with grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:59.35,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I made a choice following another's wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:01.84,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}The answer I chose was this fusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:05.90,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Which awaits us beyond this unbearable pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:11.15,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Even in the most hopeless situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:16.10,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}You always gave me a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:21.23,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}In order to protect this light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:28.27,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I'm finally prepared to become one with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:31.22,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Let's take control,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.13,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}This overwhelming power,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:38.62,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}To slash and break through the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.11,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Can you put your faith in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.77,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}So when we are able to understand one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:48.67,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}We can create countless miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:53.66,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}One day, we'll be able to rest our eyes upon the truth.
