Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:18.25,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Rada by som vedela,čo sa deje s Keita-kunom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.16,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Znel naozaj ustarostene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.69,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:31.26,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Číslo 321 patrí do tretej rady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:36.58,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Umm... pane?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.56,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Táto Tera sedí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.47,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Áno,je to tak ako sme si mysleli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.83,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Haló?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:50.16,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Bonjour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.07,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Buenos tardes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.57,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Otec!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.64,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo to robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.28,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo?Japonci?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:02.76,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,V Akibe majú limitovanú edíciu Dolfara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.08,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Ak sa nepoponáhľame vypredajú ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.15,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Hneď to bude,ukľudni sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.99,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Odpusťte mi moju nevychovanosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.00,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Mám ísť do tretieho radu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.29,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:17.07,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Japonské ženy sú krajšie ako sa hovorí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.54,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Dúfam,že vás dnes bude čakať len samé šťastie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.03,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Bože oco!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:25.68,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Nie že to povieš mame!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.56,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem veľmi pekne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.75,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Aký zaujímavý druh Teri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.62,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Som si istá,že bola v kontakte s Motosumitamov.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.32,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Neuzavrela s ňou zmluvu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.32,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to,že nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.61,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Tak potom ako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.12,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem Vám.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.86,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Umm,prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.33,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:04:00.85,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Neuzavrela zmluvu s Motosumitamov,\N ale je s ňou v kontakte... {i feel like there should be a line break in this}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.17,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Mali by sme to prešetriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.89,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.65,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to že odchádza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.34,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Sledujte ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.07,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Áno,pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.80,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem uveriť,že pán Tsubota bol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:39.43,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo mám teraz robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.34,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Keita-san,to je strašné!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:42.80,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.00,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Všetko to vyzerá tak chutne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.04,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem sa rozhodnúť čo si dám.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.42,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Vytŕča ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:55.19,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.13,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Puni-puni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.82,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Objednaj si čokoľvek len chceš.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.50,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.53,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.59,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Veľmi ti ďakujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.95,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Oh, Akane-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:52.78,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Dobrú chuť!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.84,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Hey,Puni-puni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.58,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Nemala by si ho radšej schovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.04,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.13,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.79,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Kuro porazila učiteľa,ktorý na nás zaútočil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.70,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,A potom sme utiekli zo školy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.68,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Už tam viac nemôžeme byť.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:15.52,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že by bolo lepšie, keby sme to nahlásili.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.35,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Kam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.55,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,No predsa na políciu,kde inde?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:21.11,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Veď ste predsa boli napadnutý.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.66,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.87,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Polícia nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.36,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Sú nebezpečný.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.86,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Takže polícia je v tom tiež zapletená?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.13,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.34,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Niektorý z nich išli tiež po mne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.60,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.55,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Proste som len jedla banán na ulici.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:38.24,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.54,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Ležalo ich tam veľa,tak som si jeden vzala.
