Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:22:00.81,English2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Slowly, morning creeps upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:05.70,English2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Our frozen body begins to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:12.03,English2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Our memories then awaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:17.69,English2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}And we yearn for the death that happened too soon.
